room_title: Escape room "Claustrophobia" by Number One Escape Room in Las Vegas
room_address: 1775 E Tropicana Ave Suite 100, Las Vegas, NV 89119
room_description:
You and your friend were having a drink on the Las Vegas Strip – it’s the last thing you remember. You wake up separated in a black box. Working together you have one hour to escape before the kidnapper comes back and buries you alive!
This is a two player game. If you are afraid of the dark, being confined in small places, or are CLAUSTROPHOBIC… this is not the game for you.
